<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Well-tuned" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Well-tuned,</orth> having a good sound, melodious: <cit><quote>Philomel had ended the w. warble,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1080" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1080</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the true concord of w. sounds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 8.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 8, 5</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the w. horns,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 18</bibl></cit>.
